data.description: Welcome to this inviting split level home situated on a private cul-de-sac street! This open floor plan features a comfortable living room with a charming bay window, wall to wall carpeting and flows into the formal dining room with a sliding glass door leading to the stamped concrete patio & private yard. The well equipped kitchen has a generous amount of cabinetry, stainless steel appliances including a gas range and a convenient breakfast bar for casual dining. Step down to the cozy family room with a wood burning fireplace and soft carpeting. The convenient & updated powder room and laundry are found here as well. All three bedrooms are found on the second floor and share the updated hall bath. This home has many recent updates, light filled rooms and is ideal for entertaining family and friends. don't miss out on this one!  OFFERS WILL BE ENTERTAINED UNTIL 5PM SUNDAY FEB 18TH.
